I came into the store about five minutes late and they are just now putting my pizzas in the oven. The pizza here is delicious, but do not order online and expect it to be ready on time.

I love this place!! I’ve been to the one on the west coast and I am so happy to see the pizza press here on the east coast.  Great pizza, great prices, great staff, great atmosphere! I can’t wait to come back.  Daquan is amazing!!!! He made …

DaQuan was awesome. He made our pizza and was a super star. He greeted us upon entry with a smile making us feel welcome. Being a first timer here ... he broke down the ordering process for us without hesitation. The pizza was so amazing. Best pizza in Chapel Hill!!
So many pizza places on campus Fast service, lots of toppings, price good, good beer selection. Pizza is ok but nothing special
Fantastic pizza!!

The Pizza Press has amazing pizza and a great beer selection.  I love being able to build my own pizza, especially since they have vegan options(including vegan cheese!).  It is a great spot for a quick and affordable lunch, or a date night!

Sorry Pressed the wrong star! The service here is very quick and in the fast-casual line style, a good lunch choice. Plenty of interesting options and very good toppings, plenty of seating. Be warned - this is more like a flatbread pizza than a thin crust or a regular crust, so be sure this is what you want.

The Pizza press was a life saver for me as they were open late on a weeknight.  Flat rate for a generously sized personal pizza with whatever fresh items you want.  Of particular note is the smoked, sauteed garlic.  Super tasty.  I'll be back!
Great atmosphere and awesome selection of beer.
Awesome pizzas, great crust, nice space to hang out with friends.

Quality personal pies. Their on-line ordering process is convenient if you're looking for take-out. The variety in their menu makes them an excellent choice regardless of who's in your party. Downsides include long waits at peak hours.
Wonderful little pizza place with lots of craft beer choices which you can sample first.  Great staff.
Some of the best pizza I've had in a long time. Sauce and ingredients are exceptional!

Excellent  service. Great pizza. No greasy faces.... fresh topping and amazing beer chocie. The gentleman dquan was so helpful and very knowledgeable about the press machine which I found very unique.

Pizza was delicious. Loved the variety. Options and combos are endless. We loved the huge variety of local NC craft beers on tap. The homemade ice cream sandwich is a must! Definitely our new go-to pizza joint on Franklin!

Cool pizza place with a cute newspaper theme. The pizza was good with lots of fresh toppings. $9 for a personal pizza with all the toppings you want. The crust is very thin and crispy. Lots of seating. Staff is friendly. What’s not to love?
